cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and image captioning, which are primarily related to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper discusses the use of recurrent neural networks and Bayesian priors for language representation, which are common techniques used in these sub-categories. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
